HEADER    TRANSPORT PROTEIN                       10-NOV-22   8BLO              
TITLE     HUMAN UREA TRANSPORTER UT-A (N-TERMINAL DOMAIN MODEL)                 
COMPND    MOL_ID: 1;                                                            
COMPND   2 MOLECULE: UREA TRANSPORTER 2;                                        
COMPND   3 CHAIN: A, C, B;                                                      
COMPND   4 SYNONYM: SOLUTE CARRIER FAMILY 14 MEMBER 2,UREA TRANSPORTER,KIDNEY;  
COMPND   5 ENGINEERED: YES;                                                     
COMPND   6 OTHER_DETAILS: THIS MODEL IS BASED ON THE N-TERMINAL HALF OF THE     
COMPND   7 PROTEIN UT-A. HOWEVER, UT-A CONSISTS OF TWO SIMILAR DOMAINS, AND THE 
COMPND   8 MAP IS SOMETIMES AMBIGUOUS WHETHER THE STRUCTURE IS OF THE N-TERMINAL
COMPND   9 OR C-TERMINAL HALF. MUCH OF THE MAP IS IN LINE WITH AMINO ACIDS FROM 
COMPND  10 ITS N-TERMINAL DOMAIN.                                               
